long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Staying online should be safe and comfortable, whether you're working or just surfing the internet. For that, it is necessary to delete your browser history time after time. Firstly, this action makes it much harder for hackers to collect enough of your personal information to scam you. Secondly, over time a lot of unnecessary data gets piled up in your browser eventually making it slower.

ClearHistoryFast is an excellent tool to clean, optimize and boost the performance of your device for Chrome Browser.

It will help you to:

✓ Delete your browsing history 
✓ Remove download history 
✓ Erase temporary files 
✓ Clear cookies
✓ Empty cache 
✓ Protect your privacy by cleaning up all traces of your internet activity.

You may remove or disable this extension anytime.
